name: FSymbols Draw ASCII Art
summary: An FSYMBOLS-ART file is an image created by FSymbols Draw, an online ASCII art editor. When opened in FSymbols Draw, an FYSMBOLS-ART file appears as an ASCII art image. However, FSYMBOLS-ART files are actually JSON files, which contain both a textual and PNG representation of an image.
